==Description==

The '''Std RandomColor''' command applies a random '''Diffuse Color''' to the {{PropertyView|Shape Appearance}} property of selected objects.

==Usage== 

# Select one or more objects.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View → [[Image:Std_RandomColor.svg|16px]] Random Color}} option from the menu.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Std_RandomColor.svg|16px]] Random Color}} option from the [[Tree_View|Tree View]] context menu or [[3D_View|3D View]] context menu.

==Notes==

* The {{PropertyView|Shape Appearance}} property of objects can also be changed in the [[Property_View|Property View]].


